text: "Who Says You Can't Go Home" is a song by American rock band Bon Jovi, from their ninth studio album, Have a Nice Day (2005). ==Music video== It premiered on CMT on November 24, 2005. The video debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of January 5, 2006. ==References== Category:2005 songs Category:Bon Jovi songs
